    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1954-12-31T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1952-01-01T00:00:00-05:00" n="492" subtype="editorial-note"
                type="document" xml:id="d492">
                <head>No. 492<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>Documentation concerning the role of France in the various European political,
                    military, and economic organizations is not included here. For documentation on
                    the French relationship to the North Atlantic Treaty Organization and French
                    policy toward the establishment of a European Defense Community see <ref
                        target="frus1952-54v05p1#pg_1">volume V, pages 1</ref> ff. and <ref
                        target="frus1952-54v05p1#pg_571">571</ref> ff. For documentation regarding
                    the French position in the negotiations concerning a European Political
                    Community and French policy toward the European Coal and Steel Community and the
                    Organization for European Economic Cooperation, see <ref
                        target="frus1952-54v06p1#pg_1">pages 1</ref> ff. For documentation
                    concerning French policy toward Germany and Austria, see <ref
                        target="frus1952-54v07p1">volume VII</ref>. For documentation relating to
                    French North Africa, see <ref target="frus1952-54v11p1#pg_127">volume XI, Part
                        1, pages 127</ref> ff. For extensive documentation regarding the French
                    position in Indochina, see <ref target="frus1952-54v13p1">volume XIII</ref>.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
